Have you ever gotten a style that completely messed up your healthy hair journey? 👀 Protective styles should protect! I get a lot of inquires for protective styles and some are disappointed to find out I don’t offer many of the trends 🥺 It’s healthy hair first over here! 

Well you might ask “How do I  know if a style is actually protecting my strands? 

1️⃣ It allows you to rehydrate you natural strands 

2️⃣ There is little to no tension

3️⃣ It’s not to heavy 

4️⃣ If extensions are added they are proportional to your part sizes and density, which help with not encouraging breakage 
 
5️⃣ The style doesn’t require heavy product build up

If the style is just cute and not helping you reach 2023 healthy hair goals … throw the whole style away! 🚮
